text: Agdistis bigoti is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Crete. The wingspan is 24–26 mm. The forewings are grey, as are the hindwings, although these are somewhat brighter.Eine Agdistis-Art von Kreta (Lep., Pterophoridae) ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths of Europe Category:Moths described in 1976
